replies.message: Hi Florinda. If you deleted your video you can visit www.facebook.com/friendsday to generate the video again. February 8 is the last day to edit and share your Friends Day video. Any unshared Friends Day videos will be deleted. -Jessica

Hi, Connie. In order to receive a video, you'll need to have uploaded or been tagged in a certain amount of content during your time on Facebook. If you have enough content that meets the standard to generate a video, you'll see the video at the top of your News Feed. -Rhea
